Privacy Policy
Last Updated: June 26, 2024

1. Introduction
Welcome to Silent Zone. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This privacy policy will inform you about how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our app.

2. Information We Collect
2.1 Personal Information:
We do not collect personal information such as your name, email address, or phone number.

2.2 Location Data:
We collect precise geolocation data to enable the core functionality of the app, which is to switch your phone to silent mode based on your location.
This data is only stored locally on your device and is not transmitted to our servers.

2.3 Usage Data:
We may collect non-personal data such as app usage statistics, crash reports, and performance data to improve our services.
This data is anonymized and cannot be used to identify you.

3. How We Use Your Information
3.1 To Provide Services:
To enable automatic silent mode switching based on your location.
To improve and personalize your experience with the app.

3.2 To Improve Our App:
To understand how users interact with the app and to improve its performance and functionality.

4. Data Security
We implement appropriate security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. However, please be aware that no method of transmitting or storing data is completely secure.

5. Third-Party Services
We do not share your data with third parties, except as necessary to provide our services (e.g., map services for location tracking).

6. Your Rights
You have the right to access, modify, or delete your data.
You can disable location tracking at any time through your device settings.

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new privacy policy on this page.

8. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy policy, please contact us at ciphersoft27@gmail.com.

